com.viaoa.jsp

Class OAGrid

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.jsp.OAGrid
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OAJspComponent, OAJspRequirementsInterface, Serializable

    public class OAGrid
extends Object
implements OAJspComponent, OAJspRequirementsInterface
    Grid component that will scroll equal sized cells. A template can be defined that will be filled out for each cell. Tags can then be used to embed other components, like servletImages and htmlElemets, or property paths. note: uses bootstrap, needs to be contained in a "container" or "container-fluid" parent (only one per page)
    Author:
    vvia
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
